### 3. 📋 LLC Station
**URL**: `llcstation.com`  
**Price**: 3 tiers (prices not displayed publicly — require checkout flow)

#### ✅ What's Great
| Element | Details |
|---|---|
| **"Start Your LLC From Anywhere"** | Clear, location-independent headline targeting international founders |
| **3 clean tiers** | LLC Starter → Business Builder → Diamond Business — progressive value ladder |
| **State comparison (NM vs WY)** | Side-by-side with annual costs, privacy features, use cases — very educational |
| **Multi-language** | English + Turkish + Arabic — shows commitment to MENA/South Asian markets |
| **Real testimonials w/ countries** | Lucía M. (Spain), Imran S. (Pakistan), Ahmed R. (Egypt), Fatma Nur K. (Türkiye) — diverse social proof |
| **Service breadth** | LLC + EIN + Registered Agent + Lease Agreement + ITIN + Apostille — full stack |
| **FAQ is thorough** | Answers "Do I need to be a US citizen?", "Which state?", "How long?" |

#### ❌ What's Wrong
| Issue | Impact |
|---|---|
| **No prices on homepage** | Critical mistake — price-conscious founders bounce when they can't compare |
| **"Lease Agreement" is buried** | Listed as a separate service page, not front-and-center as a differentiator |
| **Generic testimonials** | Text-only, no photos, no company names, no bank approval screenshots |
| **No "Virtual Mailbox vs Real Lease" education** | Misses the biggest objection-handling opportunity |
| **Weak CTAs** | "Get Started" everywhere — no urgency, no scarcity, no outcome-focused copy |
| **No bank-specific guidance** | "Bank Account Assistance" is vague — which banks? What's the success rate? |
| **No Stripe/checkout on site** | Redirects to external order system — adds friction |

