## 🔑 Summary: Your 3 Unfair Advantages

1. **Only full-stack provider**: LLC + ITIN + Real Residential Lease + Bank — nobody else bundles all four
2. **Cheapest residential address**: $250/qtr vs $300–$400/**month** (VirtualPostMail) or $2,000/**year** (Prime Circle)
3. **Same-day LLC**: While others take 5-7 days minimum, you file same-day with registered agent included

> [!CAUTION]
> **Don't try to compete with Doola/Firstbase on formation price** ($297–$399). Your $700 LLC is premium-positioned — justify it with same-day speed + registered agent included + ITIN eligibility. The value is in the bundle, not the individual line item.
